0e46706a06e","tid":1137782,"uid":228995,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"35ccd47e0e23210cf8407980b44d24c506a3216b","tid":1137782,"uid":63774,"like":97,"dislike":2,"score":95,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T05:20:55.000Z","msg":"因為國泰唔比百份報上機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T05:24:57.000Z","msg":"呢個係果"},{"pid":"e7c10b687a2b50656d02ed2a645ba918a4bfe830","tid":1137782,"uid":55533,"like":22,"dislike":5,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T05:29:15.000Z","msg":"方向老細俾因航空姐侮辱過"},{"pid":"da6c4b57b239e95a1884a91c556c662f3022fcc8","tid":1137782,"uid":44671,"like":93,"dislike":1,"score":92,"quote":{"pid":"6162920a449eba57dbafd9ae59bf55173588e4d9","tid":1137782,"uid":196924,"like":201,"dislike":27,"score":174,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T05:20:09.000Z","msg":"首先要因航有咁多負面消息俾佢報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T05:33:13.000Z","msg":"飛機中閃電都可以上報 其實佢有乜唔可以拎嚟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad614e127994e9e989a3b8a2a9246a643d0a70a","tid":1137782,"uid":231102,"like":173,"dislike":2,"score":171,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T05:34:58.000Z","msg":"好多都係雞毛蒜皮嘅野<br />\n但加鹽加醋寫臭晒<br />\n然後好果D直接唔報<br />\n我唔熟法律，但其實因航應該可以告因報誹謗？但一直都冇咁做<br />\n<br />\n以下節錄自網典（<a href=\"https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/東方報業集團\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.org%2Fzh%2Fwiki%2F%E6%9D%B1%E6%96%B9%E5%A0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98&d=piXtWL8Gd%2FER6BG70pbW9w9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=32a311ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/東方報業集團</a>）<br />\n<br />\n2015年7月開始，東方報業集團旗下報章，開始不斷報導國泰航空的負面新聞。有國泰員工指收到高層指示：「不要讓東方日報上到飛機」，避免乘客看到這些負面新聞。<br />\n<br />\nfb專頁 CX Secrets爆料，指事源：「大約一個月前，有位東方所謂高層嘅hand carry有成20KG，於是比avesco趕返出黎，counter同事當然要佢寄艙啦，但呢件膠層心心不忿於是講粗口鬧同事，最後驚動到supv同經理要報警。呢位膠層事後一星期竟然惡人先告狀出律師信告我地supervisor...」<br />\n<br />\n其後國泰不斷遭受「方丈」報復，網民猜測與此事有關。"},{"pid":"250c1e8acc52161dc30edf11adef4a2333c0703a","tid":1137782,"uid":35930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T05:39:15.000Z","msg":"仲有之前消防呀 郵政呀"},{"pid":"90af1c7539d4121475c274ea47bb6f6c5cd8795a","tid":1137782,"uid":76078,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"quote":{"pid":"250c1e8acc52161dc30edf11adef4a2333c0703a","tid":1137782,"uid":35930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T05:39:15.000Z","msg":"仲有之前消防呀 郵政呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T05:43:21.000Z","msg":"消防好似係因為有消防員去咗東方總部檢查消防設備 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f2be9dba8408253c21ff1e90835b6faa93fd5c","tid":1137782,"uid":31482,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T05:47:39.000Z","msg":"但同時睇出有D客都好閪，天氣差delay都投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b09fbdadadd54b04fccc8fb0ac3b32aada0213","tid":1137782,"uid":184581,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T05:51:39.000Z","msg":"睇錯泰國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"736a394121db2a7bd4388a51d8aa89531e020a55","tid":1137782,"uid":19527,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T06:05:27.000Z","msg":"仲有之前比澳門政府收地<br />\n自己啲𡃁係關口打交比人拘留<br />\n跟住就日日唱衰澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d056e90ffba6cac48f8dc59567542901a60ebfe4","tid":1137782,"uid":62850,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T06:13:01.000Z","msg":"689應該學佢開個page專數蘋果全版廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f203cffc1769f94fb765e0ea03e12aa41a8e63","tid":1137782,"uid":2054,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T06:13:03.000Z","msg":"國泰禁止運白粉？"},{"pid":"45282a1be4962dabdb7afc6895f251321e34373c","tid":1137782,"uid":42188,"like":81,"dislike":1,"score":80,"quote":{"pid":"29f2be9dba8408253c21ff1e90835b6faa93fd5c","tid":1137782,"uid":31482,"li